movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: If you are true Star Wars fan you'll love Episode i
review: If you are a true Star Wars fan then you won't care about what the critics say, and you will love the movie. I must admit that Phantom Menace does not have the charisma of the 1st 3 films, but I think of it as a side of a mountain that leads upward to the climax.
